We can talk about this at home.

36:13.540 --> 36:15.622
-Hi.
-I'm gonna stay and talk to Wyatt.

36:15.710 --> 36:18.201
Talk to him later. We got a lot of stuff
on our plate. Come on.

36:18.750 --> 36:22.004
