38:33.430 --> 38:34.966
along with two offshore accounts...

38:35.560 --> 38:37.175
one in Panama, another in Cyprus.

38:38.690 --> 38:41.261
They're numbered, just like you taught me.

38:42.320 --> 38:43.810
Every time I got paid for doing homework,

38:43.900 --> 38:47.779
