56:53.450 --> 56:55.611
No, you certainly wouldn't have.
[chuckles]

56:57.740 --> 56:59.867
-If you'll excuse me one minute.
-Yeah, sure.

57:04.040 --> 57:06.122
It's getting late.
We should get the kids home.

57:06.210 --> 57:07.086
[Marty] Yeah.

57:07.790 --> 57:10.258
I agree. Okay, um, I will...

57:10.340 --> 57:12.376
I'll finish up here, okay?

57:14.430 --> 57:15.419
See you at home.

57:21.220 --> 57:22.551
[door opens]

57:23.480 --> 57:24.515
[door closes]

58:42.220 --> 58:45.724
Don't worry about cleaning up anymore.
I'll finish it before I go.

58:47.100 --> 58:48.385
[Rachel] Well...

58:49.650 --> 58:53.609
I may not like you, but I'm not gonna
let you drink by yourself.

58:59.530 --> 59:01.191
[R&amp;B music playing on jukebox]

59:02.580 --> 59:03.979
Buddy would approve.

59:04.080 --> 59:05.286
[Rachel chuckles]

59:15.800 --> 59:17.586
Do you think I hide my emotions?

59:24.350 --> 59:28.059
I think you bury 'em in just about
the deepest grave I've ever seen.

59:33.820 --> 59:38.029
Oh, I know that it pisses off Wendy,
but I don't know what I'm supposed to do.

59:38.110 --> 59:41.694
You know, I'm trying to keep everything
from unraveling.

59:42.160 --> 59:45.652
And if I let myself get emotional...

59:49.370 --> 59:51.418
Maybe you could say exactly that.

59:52.210 --> 59:53.529
It's not that easy.

59:56.460 --> 59:57.700
Yeah, it is.

1:00:00.760 --> 1:00:02.580
You know, when Charlotte was born...

1:00:04.100 --> 1:00:06.091
do you know what my first thought was?

1:00:06.180 --> 1:00:07.306
[Rachel] Hmm?

1:00:09.520 --> 1:00:11.385
It's not okay to die.

1:00:14.730 --> 1:00:17.392
The most joyful day of my life,

1:00:17.480 --> 1:00:22.406
and I'm hit with that crushing realization

1:00:22.490 --> 1:00:25.903
